<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>POE2 BD攻略库</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: dark;
      --bg: #101113;
      --panel: #191b1f;
      --panel-2: #202329;
      --line: #343943;
      --text: #f1eee8;
      --muted: #a7a196;
      --gold: #d8a84d;
      --red: #b54e43;
      --green: #73b37a;
      --blue: #77a5c8;
      --shadow: 0 18px 55px rgba(0, 0, 0, .35);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(16, 17, 19, .65), #101113 34rem),
        url("https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/2694490/library_hero.jpg") center top / cover no-repeat fixed;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Arial, "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    button, input, select { font: inherit; }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 5;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: .85rem clamp(1rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background: rgba(16, 17, 19, .82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .8rem;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .mark {
      width: 2.25rem;
      height: 2.25rem;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(216,168,77,.6);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 25%, #74452f, #191b1f 68%);
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .brand strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .brand span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .78rem;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .4rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .88rem;
    }

    .nav a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: .45rem .65rem;
      border-radius: .35rem;
    }

    .nav a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); color: var(--text); }

    .hero {
      min-height: 24rem;
      display: grid;
      align-items: end;
      padding: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem) clamp(1rem, 4vw, 2.5rem) 2rem;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 70rem;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 12ch;
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 7vw, 5.4rem);
      line-height: .95;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      text-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.65);
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 40rem;
      margin: 1rem 0 0;
      color: #ddd6ca;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.18rem);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: .75rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 48rem;
    }

    .stat {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.11);
      background: rgba(25, 27, 31, .78);
      padding: .85rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .stat b {
      display: block;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .stat span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .78rem;
      margin-top: .25rem;
    }

    main {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: 1.5rem clamp(1rem, 4vw, 2.5rem) 3rem;
    }

    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 18rem minmax(0, 1fr) 16rem;
      gap: 1rem;
      max-width: 88rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .filters, .sidebox, .build-card, .detail-panel, .guide-card, .class-tile, .checklist-card, .faq-item, .ad-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(25, 27, 31, .96);
      border-radius: .5rem;
    }

    .filters, .ad-rail {
      position: sticky;
      top: 5rem;
    }

    .filters {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .ad-rail {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .ad-card {
      min-height: 15rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(119,165,200,.13), rgba(25,27,31,.96) 45%),
        #191b1f;
    }

    .ad-label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .ad-card h3 {
      margin: .75rem 0 .5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .ad-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #d6d0c6;
      font-size: .86rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .ad-art {
      min-height: 5.5rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      border-radius: .35rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(216,168,77,.85), rgba(181,78,67,.65)),
        url("https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/2694490/header.jpg") center / cover;
      background-blend-mode: multiply;
    }

    .ad-button {
      min-height: 2.3rem;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: .35rem;
      background: #111317;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--gold);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: .85rem;
    }

    .filters h2, .section-title h2, .sidebox h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .field {
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .78rem;
      margin-bottom: .38rem;
    }

    input, select {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 2.5rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: .35rem;
      background: #111317;
      color: var(--text);
      padding: .55rem .65rem;
      outline: none;
    }

    input:focus, select:focus { border-color: var(--gold); }

    .segmented {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: .4rem;
    }

    .chip-button {
      min-height: 2.35rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: .35rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: #111317;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .chip-button.active {
      color: #16120a;
      background: var(--gold);
      border-color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .content {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: .2rem 0;
    }

    .section-title p {
      margin: .25rem 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .9rem;
    }

    .build-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .build-card {
      min-height: 22rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .card-art {
      height: 7rem;
      background: var(--panel-2);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card-art img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      opacity: .7;
      filter: saturate(.95) contrast(1.05);
    }

    .class-badge {
      position: absolute;
      left: .75rem;
      bottom: .65rem;
      padding: .28rem .55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(16, 17, 19, .82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: .75rem;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: .95rem;
      display: flex;
      flex: 1;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .build-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .4rem;
      margin: .7rem 0;
    }

    .tag {
      padding: .25rem .45rem;
      border-radius: .28rem;
      background: #111317;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .74rem;
    }

    .tag.gold { color: var(--gold); }
    .tag.green { color: var(--green); }
    .tag.blue { color: var(--blue); }

    .desc {
      color: #d3cec5;
      font-size: .9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 .85rem;
    }

    .score-row {
      display: grid;
      gap: .45rem;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    .meter {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 4.5rem 1fr 1.8rem;
      gap: .5rem;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .75rem;
    }

    .bar {
      height: .42rem;
      background: #0d0f12;
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .bar span {
      display: block;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), var(--gold));
    }

    .open-btn {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 2.5rem;
      margin-top: .9rem;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: .35rem;
      background: #d8a84d;
      color: #17120a;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .lower {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.25fr) minmax(18rem, .75fr);
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .guide-section {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: .25rem;
    }

    .guide-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .guide-card, .checklist-card, .faq-item {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .guide-card h3, .checklist-card h3, .faq-item h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .guide-card p, .faq-item p {
      color: #d6d0c6;
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: .9rem;
      margin: .65rem 0 0;
    }

    .guide-card ul, .checklist-card ul {
      margin: .75rem 0 0;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: .86rem;
    }

    .class-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: .75rem;
    }

    .class-tile {
      min-height: 7.4rem;
      padding: .9rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background:
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(216,168,77,.13), rgba(25,27,31,.95) 42%),
        #191b1f;
    }

    .class-tile b {
      font-size: .95rem;
    }

    .class-tile span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .78rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      margin-top: .5rem;
    }

    .class-tile em {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-style: normal;
      font-size: .75rem;
      margin-top: .7rem;
    }

    .checklist-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .faq-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .detail-panel { padding: 1rem; }

    .detail-panel h3 {
      margin: 0 0 .8rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .detail-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: .7rem;
    }

    .detail-item {
      padding-bottom: .7rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }

    .detail-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .detail-item b {
      display: block;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: .82rem;
      margin-bottom: .25rem;
    }

    .detail-item span {
      color: #d6d0c6;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }

    .sidebox {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline {
      display: grid;
      gap: .75rem;
      margin-top: .85rem;
    }

    .step {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2.3rem 1fr;
      gap: .7rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .step i {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 2.2rem;
      height: 2.2rem;
      border-radius: .35rem;
      background: #111317;
      color: var(--gold);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .step b {
      display: block;
      font-size: .9rem;
      margin-bottom: .2rem;
    }

    .step span {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-size: .82rem;
    }

    .empty {
      display: none;
      border: 1px dashed var(--line);
      border-radius: .5rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer {
      max-width: 88rem;
      margin: 1.25rem auto 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .78rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .layout { grid-template-columns: 16rem minmax(0, 1fr); }
      .ad-rail {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        position: static;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
      .build-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .lower { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .guide-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .class-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 780px) {
      .topbar { align-items: flex-start; }
      .nav { display: none; }
      .hero { min-height: 25rem; }
      .stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .filters, .ad-rail { position: static; }
      .ad-rail { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .build-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .guide-grid, .class-grid, .checklist-grid, .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="mark">II</div>
      <div>
        <strong>POE2 BD攻略库</strong>
        <span>开荒、刷图、Boss与装备路线</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <nav class="nav" aria-label="主导航">
      <a href="#builds">BD构筑</a>
      <a href="#starter">开荒路线</a>
      <a href="#updates">版本观察</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <h1>Path of Exile 2 BD库</h1>
      <p>为新手和赛季玩家准备的构筑索引。先用少量高质量模板跑起来，再逐步补齐职业、装备词缀、Boss打法和版本更新。</p>
      <div class="stats" aria-label="攻略库状态">
        <div class="stat"><b>12</b><span>首批BD模板</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><b>4</b><span>核心筛选维度</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><b>6</b><span>职业入口</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><b>2026.06</b><span>内容更新位</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <div class="layout">
      <aside class="filters" aria-label="筛选器">
        <h2>筛选BD</h2>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="search">关键词</label>
          <input id="search" type="search" placeholder="技能、职业、玩法">
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="classFilter">职业</label>
          <select id="classFilter">
            <option value="all">全部职业</option>
            <option value="女巫">女巫</option>
            <option value="游侠">游侠</option>
            <option value="武僧">武僧</option>
            <option value="战士">战士</option>
            <option value="佣兵">佣兵</option>
            <option value="女术士">女术士</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label>用途</label>
          <div class="segmented" id="modeFilter">
            <button class="chip-button active" data-value="all">全部</button>
            <button class="chip-button" data-value="开荒">开荒</button>
            <button class="chip-button" data-value="刷图">刷图</button>
            <button class="chip-button" data-value="Boss">Boss</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="budgetFilter">造价</label>
          <select id="budgetFilter">
            <option value="all">全部造价</option>
            <option value="低">低造价</option>
            <option value="中">中造价</option>
            <option value="高">高造价</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="difficultyFilter">难度</label>
          <select id="difficultyFilter">
            <option value="all">全部难度</option>
            <option value="新手">新手友好</option>
            <option value="进阶">进阶</option>
            <option value="高手">高手向</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <section class="content">
        <div class="section-title" id="builds">
          <div>
            <h2>推荐BD构筑</h2>
            <p id="resultCount">正在载入构筑</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="build-grid" id="buildGrid"></div>
        <div class="empty" id="emptyState">没有匹配的BD。换个筛选条件试试。</div>

        <div class="lower">
          <section class="detail-panel" aria-live="polite">
            <h3 id="detailTitle">点击任意BD查看详情模板</h3>
            <div class="detail-list" id="detailList">
              <div class="detail-item"><b>内容结构</b><span>每个BD都会包含适合版本、核心技能、辅助宝石、天赋路线、装备词缀、开荒流程和后期提升方向。</span></div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <aside class="sidebox" id="starter">
            <h3>首批内容发布顺序</h3>
            <div class="timeline">
              <div class="step"><i>1</i><div><b>新手开荒BD Top 5</b><span>先覆盖搜索量最大的入口，让玩家快速找到能抄的方案。</span></div></div>
              <div class="step"><i>2</i><div><b>职业选择与升华</b><span>用职业页承接新手问题，再导向对应BD详情。</span></div></div>
              <div class="step"><i>3</i><div><b>装备词缀与交易清单</b><span>把“这件装备能不能用”变成可查询的清单。</span></div></div>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>

        <aside class="sidebox" id="updates">
          <h3>版本观察位</h3>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="step"><i>!</i><div><b>更新日期必须写清楚</b><span>BD类内容最怕过期。每篇攻略顶部保留版本号、更新时间、是否仍推荐。</span></div></div>
            <div class="step"><i>+</i><div><b>后续可接数据库</b><span>当前页面先用前端数据演示，之后可以迁移到 Next.js + MDX + Supabase。</span></div></div>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="guide-section" id="classes">
          <div class="section-title">
            <div>
              <h2>职业入口</h2>
              <p>每个职业都先给玩家一个明确方向，再导向可抄的BD。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="class-grid">
            <div class="class-tile"><b>游侠</b><span>远程投射物、闪避、速度优先，适合开荒和速刷。</span><em>推荐：闪电箭 / 毒雨</em></div>
            <div class="class-tile"><b>女巫</b><span>法术、召唤、诅咒路线多，新手可选控场或召唤。</span><em>推荐：冰霜 / 召唤</em></div>
            <div class="class-tile"><b>战士</b><span>近战重击、护甲、生存强，Boss表现取决于武器。</span><em>推荐：震地 / 图腾</em></div>
            <div class="class-tile"><b>武僧</b><span>连击、元素、位移节奏强，上限高但更吃操作。</span><em>推荐：冰电连击</em></div>
            <div class="class-tile"><b>佣兵</b><span>弩、榴弹、弹药切换，有不错的刷图爆发。</span><em>推荐：榴弹 / 穿甲弩</em></div>
            <div class="class-tile"><b>女术士</b><span>偏混沌、诅咒和持续伤害，适合喜欢机制流的玩家。</span><em>推荐：混沌DOT</em></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="guide-section" id="guides">
          <div class="section-title">
            <div>
              <h2>攻略栏目</h2>
              <p>这些栏目可以作为后续真实文章的固定内容池。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-grid">
